@@ -0,0 +1,21 @@
+#### Improve `with (...)` formatting (#11637 by @sosukesuzuki)
+
+<!-- prettier-ignore -->
+```scss
+// Input
+@use 'library' with (
+  $black: #222,
+  $border-radius: 0.1rem $font-family: 'Helvetica, sans-serif'
+);
+
+// Prettier stable
+@use 'library' with
+  ($black: #222, $border-radius: 0.1rem $font-family: 'Helvetica, sans-serif');
+
+// Prettier main
+@use 'library' with (
+  $black: #222,
+  $border-radius: 0.1rem $font-family: 'Helvetica, sans-serif'
+);
+
+```
